"async/alt!" is a transducer that can be used to alter the contents of a channel.
It takes a channel and a transducer.
It applies the transducer to each item in the channel.
It then puts the result of the transducer on a new channel.

The transducer must be a function that takes a single argument and returns a value.
The value is put on the new channel.

